description: I don't know exaclty what version is the last one, but this one is from the Bachsmith DLC pack of Rocksmith 2014, using a software that converts Rocksmith files to GP5, ensuring complete accuracy. I haven't tempered with instrumentation, some parts should be distorted while some parts clean, if anyone wanna do this, feel free.
title: Edvard Grieg - In The Hall Of The Mountain King (Cover)
